}

========================================================================================

I found you can color the bullets by just using "color:#ddd;" on the "li" item itself.

li{
    color:#ff0000;    
    list-style:square;                
}
a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color:#00ff00;
}

a:hover {
    background-color: #ddd;
}


